  "texts": [
    "Participants 9 and 16 demonstrated awareness of their phased progress and expressed the desire to maintain a positive mindset and high level of proficiency through their individualized creation loop for learning habits.",
    "Participants 9",
    "I'm still a little bit interested; for example, I can hear fluently, I'm still quite happy and have a sense of achievement, but I think it's more to do with study habits, because I'm a serious person and strive for perfection.",
    "So every time I do it (listening proficiency), I focus on quality and quantity.",
    "Participant 16 emphasized that the development of listening proficiency as a habit relies on several factors."
  ]
